arguments.name: Array
arguments.description: The array or range of values to trim and average.

arguments.name: Percent
arguments.description: The fractional number of data points to exclude from the calculation. For example, if percent = 0.2, 4 points are trimmed from a data set of 20 points (20 x 0.2): 2 from the top and 2 from the bottom of the set.
